    "Therefore, in a broad sense, a service can be seen as a response to demand.",
    "Services are built toward business objectives and are invoked between each other through APIs.",
    "Network function: an NF is composed of multiple services that perform related functions.",
    "Service framework: a service framework is a universal service that can host other services, enable registration, discovery, and authorization of services, and scale and customize them for different use cases.",
    "The 5G service framework is centered around the network repository function (NRF) and service communication proxy (SCP)."
